creator: Phillips Auctioneers
descriptionHtml:
Phillips auction house brings a fresh contemporary focus to the defining aesthetic movements of the last two centuries, with a specialized knowledge in what's happening right now. Our international sales are the building blocks of a great collection, for both savvy collectors and auction-curious newcomers alike.

Now, participating in our auctions is easier than ever. The Phillips app allows you to browse upcoming sales, track your favorite lots and place bids in our live auctions from anywhere on your Android device. Welcome to the first truly mobile auction saleroom.
descriptionShort: Browse upcoming sales, track your favorite lots, and place bids in our auctions.
